408549fc9b7f674256ab6cd968f931b008e69f15.text_content:
Welcome to andOTP, this wizard will guide you through the initial setup. Please pay attention and read carefully otherwise you could lose data! 

Don't worry, you can still change any of the options later in the Settings.

1fab09a4fb1be89de9cd44b14298479741a95cee.text_content: To ensure the security of your accounts andOTP only stores them in encrypted data files. Here you can choose which method of encryption will be used.

This method will encrypt your data with a key generated from a password or PIN. The main advantage here is that this will work with external backup solutions (like Titanium) and is much less failure-prone than the KeyStore. However, you will have to enter your credentials every time you start andOTP.

84c7009bffcb66d200fcdba0ac9df65ce9ae52f7.text_content: Here you can setup an authentication to lock andOTP. Since you have chosen Password / PIN as encryption method you need to set either a password or a PIN to proceed.
Please set a password to continue!

e435546f20990aafb95509e1928aa9bf69418e04.text_content: Here you can setup an authentication to lock andOTP. Since you have chosen Password / PIN as encryption method you need to set either a password or a PIN to proceed.
The password needs to be at least 6 characters long!

86ff064bce84fb8590e37a7c94947e2adc3c7d36.text_content: Here you can setup an authentication to lock andOTP. Since you have chosen Password / PIN as encryption method you need to set either a password or a PIN to proceed.
Please confirm your password to continue!

1bea41187d94aa92c0ecddab1c7ef6867272012d.text_content: Here you can setup an authentication to lock andOTP. Since you have chosen Password / PIN as encryption method you need to set either a password or a PIN to proceed.

17a5c727578fd4026221d0087a4ffe5383cd352f.text_content: Your settings have been saved, you are all set to use andOTP now!

0f9838f2810e0601d1f0468046d24671fa9b25a3.text_content: Please confirm your authentication to generate the new encryption key!
